 Vĩ Nghiệp</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%E1%BB%ABa-v%C4%83n-H%C3%A0-B%E1%BA%AFc-ch%C6%B0-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-ti%E1%BA%BFt-%C4%91%E1%BB%99-nh%E1%BA%ADp-tri%E1%BB%81u-hoan-h%E1%BB%89-kh%E1%BA%A9u-h%C3%A0o-tuy%E1%BB%87t-c%C3%BA-k%E1%BB%B3-10/poem-FJTSkMljrwlnQxVOiRZXUg">Thừa văn Hà Bắc chư đạo tiết độ nhập triều, hoan hỉ khẩu hào tuyệt cú kỳ 10 - 承聞河北諸道節度入朝歡喜口號絕句其十</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/Ti%E1%BB%85n-Tri%E1%BB%87u-Phong-th%C3%A1i-th%C3%BA-H%C3%A0-Thi%E1%BA%BFu-Trai-th%C4%83ng-b%E1%BB%95-B%C3%ACnh-Thu%E1%BA%ADn-%C3%A1n-s%C3%A1t-s%E1%BB%A9/poem-UOMhoOzes0J1zh7vR21Wgw">Tiễn Triệu Phong thái thú Hà Thiếu Trai thăng bổ Bình Thuận án sát sứ - 餞肇豐太守何少齊陞補平順按察使</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-h%C3%A0n-l%C3%A2m-Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%C6%B0-m%C3%A3-Nam-H%E1%BA%A3i-l%E1%BA%B7c-bi/poem-4pTVYA-Tfj42JjTCNVDFhQ">Tống hàn lâm Trương tư mã Nam Hải lặc bi - 送翰林張司馬南海勒碑</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/Y%E1%BA%BFt-Kim-m%C3%B4n-Ho%C3%A0i-c%E1%BB%91-c%C6%B0-t%C3%A1c/poem-qqbb5usxNqCEMjqKVxS7mQ">Yết Kim môn - Hoài cố cư tác - 謁金門－懷故居作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/author-uhvQQ4xb005il66VwoQrSQ">Tô Tường</a>)<br></div>	</div>
